Class GeneratedArtefact

java.lang.Object
  de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.controller.datageneration.GeneratedArtefact

public class GeneratedArtefact
extends java.lang.Object

This class holds the artefacts ready to get serialized into a XML file. Artefacts stored in here passed the test data generation process and and wait to get written out.

May/13/09
